    "Name": "Hyaenodont",
    "Details": "The Hyaenodont C configuration features a Hyper PPC equipped with a Particle Recycler Module for enhanced energy efficiency, supported by two Early Clan Improved Gauss Rifles for reliable, high-impact ballistic fire. It also mounts an Improved AC/10 with an Ares Target Projection Suite attachment, firing HEAR ammunition to increase damage and sensor visibility on critical hits. Integrated with the PHI Suite, this variant excels at versatile mid- to long-range engagements, combining powerful direct fire with advanced targeting support for coordinated lance strikes.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable Weapons</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.28</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Omni</color>",
